<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>You can <a rel="external" href="https://public.govdelivery.com/accounts/UKHMRCED/subscriber/new?preferences=true#tab1" class="govuk-link">sign up for email alerts about live and recorded webinars, YouTube videos and online guidance</a>.</p>

<p>If you register for a webinar, you:</p>

<ul>
  <li>must register and sign in 5 minutes before it starts</li>
  <li>can ask questions using the on-screen text box</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="extension-to-the-coronavirus-job-retention-scheme-and-flexible-furloughing">Extension to the Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme and flexible furloughing</h2>

<p>Register for the <a rel="external" href="https://attendee.gotowebinar.com/rt/8528021499696163331?source=June-HMRC-GOV" class="govuk-link">next live webinar about the extension to the Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme and flexible furloughing</a>.</p>

<p>This webinar gives an overview of the changes to the scheme and more information on:</p>

<ul>
  <li>changes to the scheme</li>
  <li>the Job Retention Bonus</li>
  <li>flexible furloughing</li>
  <li>who can claim</li>
  <li>making a claim</li>
</ul>

<p>Watch a YouTube video about the extension to the Coronavirus Job Retention Scheme and flexible furloughing.</p>

<p>Watch a <a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w7NDIqPfP_w" class="govuk-link">YouTube video</a>.</p>

<h2 id="self-employment-income-support-scheme--claiming-the-second-grant">Self-Employment Income Support Scheme – claiming the second grant</h2>

<p><a rel="external" href="https://attendee.gotowebinar.com/rt/6004260784831494413?source=August-HMRC-GOV" class="govuk-link">Register for the next live webinar</a> about the Self-Employment Income Support Scheme – claiming the second grant.</p>

<p>This webinar will tell you:</p>

<ul>
  <li>how to claim the second grant in the Self-Employed Income Support Scheme</li>
  <li>who is eligible</li>
  <li>the amount you can claim</li>
  <li>what other support is available</li>
</ul>

<p>Watch a YouTube video about the Self-Employment Income Support Scheme – claiming the second grant.</p>

<p>Watch a <a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?reload=9&v=58KrEskD0sM&list=PL8EcnheDt1zhTsyhT9ak3xiXnmlvbHJJV&index=10" class="govuk-link">YouTube video</a></p>

<h2 id="self-employment-income-support-scheme--universal-credit-and-child-benefit">Self-Employment Income Support Scheme – Universal Credit and Child Benefit</h2>

<p>Watch a YouTube video about the Self Employment Income Support Scheme, Universal Credit, and Child Benefit.</p>

<p>This video takes you through:</p>

<ul>
  <li>the Self-Employment Income Support Scheme – who it’s for and how much you may be able to claim</li>
  <li>Universal Credit – who it’s for, how much you may be entitled to and how to claim</li>
  <li>Child Benefit – who can claim and how to do so</li>
</ul>

<p>Watch a <a rel="external" href="https://youtu.be/HuPKSVliuyk" class="govuk-link">YouTube video</a></p>

<h2 id="self-employment-income-support-scheme--what-has-changed-for-parents">Self-Employment Income Support Scheme – what has changed for parents</h2>

<p>Watch a YouTube video about what has changed for parents on the Self-Employment Income Support Scheme.</p>

<p>This video gives an overview of recent changes to the Self-Employment Income Support Scheme which mean some parents who were not eligible to claim under the scheme before, may now be able to claim, providing they meet other standard eligibility.</p>

<p>Watch a <a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pIgPym1UxDc&list=PL8EcnheDt1zhTsyhT9ak3xiXnmlvbHJJV&index=9" class="govuk-link">YouTube video</a></p>

<h2 id="statutory-sick-pay-ssp-rebate-scheme">Statutory Sick Pay (<abbr title="Statutory Sick Pay">SSP</abbr>) Rebate Scheme</h2>

<p>Register for the next <a rel="external" href="https://register.gotowebinar.com/rt/3667545685723120643?source=Apr-HMRC-GOV" class="govuk-link">live webinar about the Coronavirus Statutory Sick Pay Rebate Scheme</a>.</p>

<p>This webinar gives an overview of the <abbr title="Statutory Sick Pay">SSP</abbr> Rebate Scheme, including:</p>

<ul>
  <li>who can claim</li>
  <li>when to start paying <abbr title="Statutory Sick Pay">SSP</abbr>
</li>
  <li>employees you can claim for</li>
  <li>making a claim</li>
  <li>keeping records and more</li>
</ul>

<p>Watch a YouTube video about the Coronavirus Statutory Sick Pay Rebate Scheme.</p>

<p>Watch a <a rel="external" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uXAUQ7BEebo&list=PL8EcnheDt1zhTsyhT9ak3xiXnmlvbHJJV&index=4" class="govuk-link">YouTube video</a></p>

<h2 id="other-help-available">Other help available</h2>

<p>Use <a rel="external" href="https://www.tax.service.gov.uk/ask-hmrc/virtual-assistant/support-for-coronavirus?VA=GOVUK" class="govuk-link">HMRC’s digital assistant</a> to find more information about the coronavirus support schemes.</p>

</div>
